1
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,700
Have you ever heard about that

2
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,580
the cliff of a snow mountain

3
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,220
once fascinated numerous people?

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:24,140
Legend has it that,

5
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,940
there were treasures at the peak

6
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:32,860
but also there was a bottomless chasm hidden over there.

7
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:37,900
The smart, the fool

8
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,740
and the kind people,

9
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:47,220
all are familiar to you.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,660
On the mountainside, on the cliff,

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,580
on the cloud,

12
00:00:54,980 --> 00:01:00,100
and in the human world,

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:19,220
snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.

14
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,980
Joy of Life Season 1

15
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,900
Episode 22

16
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:40,310
Uncle.

17
00:01:42,310 --> 00:01:44,190
What's up, Uncle Wuzhu?

18
00:01:46,870 --> 00:01:47,550
Uncle.

19
00:01:50,830 --> 00:01:51,480
Uncle.

20
00:01:53,230 --> 00:01:53,870
Uncle Wuzhu.

21
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:03,590
Uncle! Uncle!

22
00:02:08,390 --> 00:02:09,190
I think I remember

23
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:10,390
where the Taiping Residence is.

24
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:12,830
Where is it?

25
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:18,800
2.5 km east of the city.

26
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,910
The key to my mom's box

27
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:23,800
might be hidden

28
00:02:24,110 --> 00:02:25,520
in the Taiping Residence.

29
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,440
If we find it,

30
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:28,190
you may get your memory back.

31
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,190
Let's go there tomorrow.

32
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,390
No, I can't.

33
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,390
If I rush to

34
00:02:32,390 --> 00:02:33,080
the Taiping Residence now,

35
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,360
I will draw a lot of attention.

36
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,440
Then I will go.

37
00:02:35,550 --> 00:02:36,190
Neither can you.

38
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:38,470
I have an idea.

39
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:41,000
But I need a few days for preparation.

40
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,240
For this trip out of the capital,

41
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:45,750
we'll need a lot of company.

42
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,270
Why?

43
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,880
Crowds can make it easier

44
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:54,360
to hide the truth.

45
00:02:56,270 --> 00:03:04,160
Bravo! Bravo! Bravo!

46
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,000
We've made a large purchase of paper,

47
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,550
and the unit price is three qians higher than expected.

48
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:13,550
Luckily, we've cut the number of servants.

49
00:03:13,550 --> 00:03:14,670
That might make up to it.

50
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,030
Don't think about this on a trip out of the city.

51
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:18,830
What's your problem, Fan Xian? Give it to me.

52
00:03:20,390 --> 00:03:21,030
What should you call him?

53
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:22,670
Brother.

54
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:23,600
Give it to me!

55
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,960
You don't have to worry about that.

56
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,600
Then who will take care of it?

57
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,720
Our bookstore is going to open soon.

58
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,750
You don't write books.

59
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:31,800
You only fool around.

60
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:33,910
Who asked to come along?

61
00:03:36,110 --> 00:03:37,390
I just want to keep an eye on him.

62
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:52,000
Your Excellency, the girls are in front.

63
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:02,520
You can't go inside!

64
00:04:17,670 --> 00:04:18,830
Ling'er also wants to go for an outing.

65
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:20,440
Do you mind

66
00:04:20,790 --> 00:04:21,950
if we can go out together?

67
00:04:23,350 --> 00:04:24,070
I don't mind.

68
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,720
More people, more fun.

69
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,830
I don't know how you made it.

70
00:04:29,110 --> 00:04:30,320
The northern side of our country is at war,

71
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:31,350
but His Majesty actually

72
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:32,640
agreed on us coming out.

73
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,200
We should enjoy life

74
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,480
even when the war is intense.

75
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:38,110
So the enemies can feel our confidence

76
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,880
in winning the war.

77
00:04:40,350 --> 00:04:41,070
You're talking nonsense.

78
00:04:42,110 --> 00:04:42,830
Walking out more often

79
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:43,830
is good for your health.

80
00:04:44,550 --> 00:04:45,640
Whatever you say.

81
00:04:47,790 --> 00:04:48,790
Really?

82
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:57,950
I miss you.

83
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:02,070
If only we could get married sooner.

84
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:03,920
Then we can be together every day.

85
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,640
Fine. Fine. Fine.

86
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,160
I'll take another carriage.

87
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,550
Enjoy yourselves.

88
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:15,920
Lady Ye,

89
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,640
how can you get off alone,

90
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:18,950
leaving My Lady alone with that...

91
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,350
If I stay for another minute, I'm gonna puke.

92
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,040
If you can tolerate that,

93
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,920
you can go inside.

94
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:25,670
Can you be gentle?

95
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:26,760
You...

96
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,760
How come it's you, tigress?

97
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,950
Where do you hide my brother?

98
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,480
Lady Fan Ruoruo,

99
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:35,550
someone acted so shamelessly

100
00:05:35,550 --> 00:05:36,200
in Princess Lin's carriage.

101
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:37,510
It's really awkward

102
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,600
for me to stay there.

103
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:39,920
If you don't mind,

104
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:41,950
I will stay with you.

105
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,670
Come over and take a seat.

106
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:48,830
Sister!

107
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:51,320
How can you let her

108
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,440
stay with us?

109
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,160
You must protect me!

110
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:59,600
Sister, you must protect me!

111
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:08,160
Your trick works. Are you happy now?

112
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,640
Those words are from the bottom of my heart.

113
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,640
Why aren't we leaving?

114
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,200
There's one more person to come.

115
00:06:23,110 --> 00:06:24,040
One more person?

116
00:06:34,350 --> 00:06:35,720
Xianxian!

117
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,920
Dabao!

118
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,390
Wan'er!

119
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:40,880
I invited him.

120
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,350
Dabao, come over now.

121
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,480
I'll stay here.

122
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:48,720
Dad said,

123
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,320
I should... I should...

124
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:50,790
I should...

125
00:06:50,790 --> 00:06:51,670
give

126
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:52,920
Xianxian and Wan'er

127
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,760
more private space.

128
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:56,110
Good boy! You're the best.

129
00:06:56,350 --> 00:06:58,320
Dabao, sit well in the carriage.

130
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,350
Let's go for an outing.

131
00:06:59,550 --> 00:07:01,160
Xianxian, you really know how to play.

132
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,440
Don't call me Xianxian.

133
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:05,640
OK.

134
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,550
Xianxian!

135
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:19,200
The war is on.

136
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,760
Yan Ruohai is at the border

137
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:22,440
dealing with secret information.

138
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:23,720
He's terribly busy.

139
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,160
God blesses Nanqing.

140
00:07:25,550 --> 00:07:27,440
We're doing really well in the war.

141
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:32,390
But recently,

142
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,880
officials from the Six Ministries start to clamor,

143
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,670
advocating that

144
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,040
we should capture Beiqi

145
00:07:39,670 --> 00:07:40,670
at one fling.

146
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:42,830
Who started it?

147
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:45,320
We don't know yet.

148
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,440
But officials who take part

149
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,160
are from Six Ministries.

150
00:07:49,550 --> 00:07:50,600
Investigate them thoroughly.

151
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,390
Head...

152
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,670
The "gnawing-away" scheme

153
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,270
set by His Majesty is the safest.

154
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,390
The war is about to end.

155
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:02,600
Whoever advocate capturing Beiqi

156
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,550
are traitors.

157
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,350
Many officials from our Office

158
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:08,390
also hold this view.

159
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:09,510
In their opinion,

160
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,230
it's the best chance to unify the whole world.

161
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,480
Investigate them, punish them,

162
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,320
or even kill them if you have to.

163
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,880
Yes.

164
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:28,830
Many people hope to capture Beiqi with one blow.

165
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:33,470
The louder they advocate, the sooner they'll give up!

166
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,000
Is Fan Xian OK?

167
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,030
He goes for an outing

168
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:37,880
with Lin Wan'er.

169
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,200
Why don't you go along?

170
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,150
I can't.

171
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:41,470
If anything happens to you,

172
00:08:41,470 --> 00:08:42,400
I won't be able to get back.

173
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,550
How can anything happen to me?

174
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,670
Recently,

175
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:48,440
there's been a secret voice against
you in the Investigator's Office.

176
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:49,320
Someone is fed up with

177
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,550
your control.

178
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:53,960
Who might that be?

179
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,440
If I know, I'll kill him.

180
00:08:56,590 --> 00:08:59,520
Chen Pingping, be careful about the people around you.

181
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:11,640
What's up?

182
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:13,790
The Head wants to investigate

183
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:16,760
which officials from the Six Ministries advocate war.

184
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,840
That's the job of your division.

185
00:09:20,470 --> 00:09:21,230
Recently,

186
00:09:21,590 --> 00:09:23,790
there have been officials meeting secretly everywhere,

187
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:25,440
planning to submit a joint memorial

188
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,110
for wiping out Beiqi at one blow.

189
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:28,910
You really should carry out a thorough investigation.

190
00:09:30,350 --> 00:09:31,440
Last night

191
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:32,790
in the residence of the Assistant
Minister of Ministry of Penalty,

192
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,030
someone from our Investigator's Office

193
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:36,150
was also there.

194
00:09:39,470 --> 00:09:40,200
Do you know

195
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,470
what you've been doing?

196
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,960
My son is still at the capital of Beiqi.

197
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:46,790
The earlier Beiqi is captured,

198
00:09:47,230 --> 00:09:48,030
the sooner

199
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:49,760
he can be safe.

200
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,790
I haven't told the Head about it.

201
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:53,400
It's not too late to stop.

202
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,350
With the "gnawing-away" scheme,

203
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:56,790
how many years will it be

204
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:57,960
to capture Beiqi.

205
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:00,200
We don't have a say in this.

206
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,910
Whatever I do,

207
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:03,400
I do it for Nanqing.

208
00:10:03,590 --> 00:10:04,710
So does the Head.

209
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:05,590
He's old.

210
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,280
Enough!

211
00:10:07,230 --> 00:10:08,710
Don't make me arrest you myself!

212
00:11:12,230 --> 00:11:13,640
Can I poke it?

213
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,230
No! It will bite you.

214
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,670
Is it poisonous?

215
00:11:19,590 --> 00:11:20,520
I don't know.

216
00:11:23,470 --> 00:11:25,470
Look, there's another hole here.

217
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,640
Will it

218
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,710
hide something inside?

219
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:29,790
Childish!

220
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:35,080
Poke it! Poke it!

221
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,030
Dabao.

222
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:42,790
Don't play with worms.

223
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,790
How about learning

224
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:45,440
some self-defense moves from me?

225
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,030
Self-defense moves!

226
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,230
Is that fun?

227
00:11:50,350 --> 00:11:51,030
Dabao.

228
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:57,080
Don't talk to her.

229
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:58,670
Don't.

230
00:11:59,110 --> 00:12:01,550
She is a tigress.

231
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:04,000
She eats people. She's horrible.

232
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,280
She's not.

233
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:06,880
She's Wan'er's friend.

234
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,000
She's not scary.

235
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,080
I'm Fan Xian's younger brother.

236
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,150
Don't you believe me?

237
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,590
Xianxian?

238
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,960
If you don't believe me,

239
00:12:18,350 --> 00:12:20,320
don't you believe Xianxian?

240
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:24,280
Sister,

241
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:25,710
he told me you're a tigress.

242
00:12:25,710 --> 00:12:26,350
Will you eat people?

243
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:27,000
What?

244
00:12:28,470 --> 00:12:29,910
Fan Sizhe, do you need a good beat?

245
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:30,550
I didn't say that.

246
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:31,110
Stop!

247
00:12:31,110 --> 00:12:32,590
Hurry up! Run!

248
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:33,790
Little one, just run!

249
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:34,400
Stop!

250
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:35,590
The tigress will eat you.

251
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,790
Hurry up and run! Hurry up and run!

252
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:37,400
I didn't expect them

253
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,230
to have fun together.

254
00:12:40,470 --> 00:12:41,840
Dabao still retains childlike innocence.

255
00:12:42,350 --> 00:12:43,590
He's willing to come out with you,

256
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,910
which means he really trusts you.

257
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,440
We will be family in future.

258
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,080
Thank you.

259
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,030
Thank me for what?

260
00:12:55,350 --> 00:12:56,110
I know that

261
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,910
my second brother's funeral is being
held in the Prime Minister's mansion.

262
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,200
As a bastard daughter,

263
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,280
I can't go there.

264
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:06,550
Your father said

265
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:07,640
he doesn't want Dabao

266
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,670
to stay in the mansion, either.

267
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,030
He said since your bother is gone,

268
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,440
no need to make the living ones suffer.

269
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:14,840
Stop!

270
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:16,590
You really need a good beat!

271
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:19,840
But he's my second brother after all.

272
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:35,710
Where's Ruoruo?

273
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,030
Where is she?

274
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:39,440
She's probably idling around.

275
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:40,230
Let her be.

276
00:13:41,030 --> 00:13:41,790
Have some fruit.

277
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,200
Your Highness,

278
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:11,230
the three-day punishment is over.

279
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,640
Read these days' information

280
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:17,710
to me.

281
00:14:18,030 --> 00:14:18,710
Yes.

282
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,150
Recently,

283
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:25,520
there have been hot debates in the imperial court.

284
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:27,470
We've achieved a complete victory in the war against Beiqi.

285
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,400
Now, many officials from different ministries

286
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:33,110
want to submit a joint memorial

287
00:14:33,230 --> 00:14:34,760
to advocate capturing Beiqi at one blow.

288
00:14:36,230 --> 00:14:37,960
The Second Prince is contacting the Ministry of War.

