321
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:56,520
Let me help you.

322
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,710
What have you got?

323
00:16:10,520 --> 00:16:11,670
Don't tell anyone

324
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:13,110
about my visit,

325
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,110
