336
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:48,760
Do you feel anything wrong?

337
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,030
Nothing.

338
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:53,080
Nothing wrong.

339
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:05,560
Got it!

340
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,230
Put it down! Put it down! Put it down!

