00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:19,920
the Lin family?

367
00:18:22,950 --> 00:18:26,470
I still don't know who killed Gong'er.

368
00:18:28,110 --> 00:18:29,160
I can trust the Lin family

369
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:30,640
to an outsider.

370
00:18:31,470 --> 00:18:33,830
But I must

