00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:52,710
The day the Second Young Master was killed,

379
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:55,280
Fan Xian really didn't leave the capital city.

380
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,280
I have a suspicion.

381
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:04,920
What if there's a hidden martial arts master

382
00:19:06,230 --> 00:19:07,520
by Fan Xian's side,

383
00:19:08,430 --> 00:19:09,280
a master who could

