00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:14,560
Fan Xian was inside the capital city,

386
00:19:14,830 --> 00:19:17,070
but that martial arts master killed Gong'er instead.

387
00:19:18,110 --> 00:19:19,160
According to Si Lili,

388
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,000
she didn't tell Fan Xian

389
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:21,920
the secret of the Second Young Master.

390
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:24,880
Her words don't matter.

391
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:27,110
As long as evidences show that

392
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:28,830
there's a peerless martial arts master

393
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:29,680
around Fan Xian,

394
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:31,230
I can confirm that

