535
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:40,950
Boss!

536
00:26:41,230 --> 00:26:41,920
What's up?

537
00:26:42,430 --> 00:26:43,070
He left.

538
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:43,710
Who left?

539
00:26:43,950 --> 00:26:45,950
Our lady and a young man

540
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:47,590
