641
00:31:26,280 --> 00:31:27,160
Uncle!

642
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:32,560
Unbelievable!

643
00:31:39,310 --> 00:31:40,760
Boss, why not cover your face?

644
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:42,920
