645
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:46,710
It's been a while. No one has shown up.

646
00:31:46,710 --> 00:31:48,310
Should we let him go?

647
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:54,520
Are we going to see the Prime Minister?

648
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,760
