652
00:32:03,310 --> 00:32:04,710
We can't let him go.

653
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:06,640
What should we do?

654
00:32:08,710 --> 00:32:09,830
How could I know?

655
00:32:18,470 --> 00:32:19,350
Nothing happens.

656
00:32:21,540 --> 00:32:24,580
