712
00:40:25,150 --> 00:40:27,000
I'm afraid he was trying to lure the guards away.

713
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:29,280
So I take the liberty to see whether Your Majesty is OK.

714
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:30,280
I'm fine.

715
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:43,870
If Your Majesty is fine,

716
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,000
then I'm relieved.

717
00:40:54,120 --> 00:40:55,390
One more thing.

718
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:57,670
Your Majesty, do you need anything to eat?

719
00:40:58,910 --> 00:41:00,560
I've finished my meal.

720
00:41:18,040 --> 00:41:19,560
This is Yan Xiaoyi,

721
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:20,390
Director of Imperial Guards,

722
00:41:21,910 --> 00:41:23,120
a martial arts master above the Ninth Dan.

723
00:41:23,710 --> 00:41:26,560
He's only one step away from the Great Master.

724
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:30,800
I almost forgot that

725
00:41:30,800 --> 00:41:32,320
martial arts master above the Ninth Dan

726
00:41:32,870 --> 00:41:34,080
can distinguish two people by breaths

727
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:36,430
through the wall.

728
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,080
Put down your arrow.

729
00:41:39,600 --> 00:41:41,520
I'm not under threat.

730
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:45,470
This is Fan Xian, Chief Musician of
the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

731
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:47,280
When he leaves later,

732
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:48,910
let him pass.

733
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:51,280
Yes.

734
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:52,630
Also,

735
00:41:53,280 --> 00:41:55,230
pass on my verbal instruction to the Imperial Guards.

736
00:41:55,600 --> 00:41:56,870
When I leave for the capital city,

737
00:41:57,120 --> 00:41:58,430
send a battalion

738
00:41:58,670 --> 00:41:59,600
to guard this place.

739
00:42:00,710 --> 00:42:01,560
From now on,

740
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,600
no one shall

741
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:05,670
get near this residence.

742
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:07,080
Yes.

743
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:18,950
You're lucky that you're still alive.

744
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:20,630
You should know that martial arts master above the Ninth Dan

745
00:42:20,630 --> 00:42:21,840
can hear another man's breath

746
00:42:21,840 --> 00:42:24,080
through the wall.

747
00:42:24,390 --> 00:42:25,910
They can figure out my position

748
00:42:25,910 --> 00:42:28,000
