752
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:39,760
They're beyond common sense.

753
00:43:05,780 --> 00:43:09,100
In the river of history,

754
00:43:09,380 --> 00:43:12,300
time goes round and round.

755
00:43:15,660 --> 00:43:18,660
Memories about the former and present lives

756
00:43:19,020 --> 00:43:22,540
